Package frc.robot

Class Constants.RobotConfig

java.lang.Object
frc.robot.Constants.RobotConfig
Enclosing class:
Constants
public class Constants.RobotConfig extends Object
RobotConfig contains configuration for the robot's drive system and pods. Includes pod configs, kinematics, and reset logic.
